<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=583&amp;p=606#p606"><![CDATA[
1/16(Sun. on-line meeting only) 11 Crazy Ways The Weather Influences Your Health and Behavior<br />&amp; Understanding Foreign Cultures By Eating Their Food (Shuman))<br /><br /><br />加入 Zoom 會議<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... NKSU5MQT09<br /><br />會議 ID：929 8726 6213<br />密碼：112233<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Presentation 1<br />8:00-8:10 pm Break<br />8:10-8:40: Session 2 Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation 2<br /><br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session I<br />11 Crazy Ways The Weather Influences Your Health and Behavior<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/weather-and-health_us_570facd9e4b08a2d32b92ae9">https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/we ... 2d32b92ae9</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />1. Please name one or two points of view in this article that you could not agree with more and explain why.<br />2. Do you or your family members have any health problems when weather changes? (Such us sneezing, stuffy nose, chapped lips, achy joints, headache, high/low blood pressure and so on.)<br />3. Are you a hot weather person or a cold weather lover? Why? (What are your favorite and least favorite seasons of the year? What makes it unique or different from other seasons to you?)<br /><br />Session II<br />Understanding Foreign Cultures By Eating Their Food<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.newsweek.com/understanding-foreign-cultures-eating-their-food-92593">http://www.newsweek.com/understanding-f ... food-92593</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />1. What is the food style that you most prefer, Chinese, Japanese, Thai, or western style?<br />2. Do you trust in Michelin Stars? Have you ever try the restaurant that Michelin guide to recommend to you? Please share your opinion or experience.<br />3. Food culture depends on what is the crops we plant, so do you believe in it shape us to be different with western people even the Africa people?<br />4. In many cases, foreign cuisine would change the flavor to makes acceptable to local. How about you? Do you like to taste the original or the changed flavor?<br />5. Do you think the night market foods can represent Taiwan's food feature? Please share your thought with everyone.<br /><br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=872">Shuman</a> — Sun Jan 09, 2022 9:07 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
